00031 template <typename T, int Size>
00032 void DumpStats(const BList<T, Size>& blist)
00033 {
00034   BListStats stats = blist.GetStats();
00035 
00036   int nodes = stats.NodeCount;
00037   int items = stats.ItemCount;
00038   int asize = stats.ArraySize;
00039 
00040   double ipn;
00041   if (nodes)
00042     ipn = static_cast<double>(items) / static_cast<double>(nodes);
00043   else
00044     ipn = 0;
00045 
00046   double util = ipn / static_cast<double>(asize) * 100;
00047 
00048   std::cout << "Asize: " << asize << std::endl;
00049   std::cout << "Items: " << items << std::endl;
00050   std::cout << "Nodes: " << nodes << std::endl;
00051   std::cout << "Average items per node: " << ipn << std::endl;
00052   std::cout << "Node utilization: " << std::setprecision(3) << util << "%" << std::endl;
00053   std::cout << std::endl;
00054 }

00056 template <typename T, int Size>
00057 void DumpList(const BList<T, Size>& blist, bool flat = false)
00058 {
00059   const typename BList<T, Size>::BNode *node = blist.GetHead();
00060   int count = 0;
00061   if (flat)
00062     std::cout << "List: ";
00063   while (node)
00064   {
00065     if (!flat)
00066       std::cout << "Node " << std::setw(3) << ++count << " (" << std::setw(2) << node->count << "): ";
00067 
00068     for (int i = 0; i < node->count; i++)
00069     {
00070       std::cout << node->values[i] << " ";
00071     }
00072 
00073     if (!flat)
00074       std::cout << std::endl;
00075     node = node->next;
00076   }
00077   std::cout << std::endl;
